The '''SS-19 cargo transport''' was a model of light [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] produced by the [[Corellian Engineering Corporation/Legends|Corellian Engineering Corporation]]. [[Armanda Durkin]], CEO of the [[Notsub Shipping Company]], owned a highly modified SS-19 named ''[[Vengeful Sandstorm]]''.

